Package com.programmerdan.minecraft.civspy

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CivSpy
    CivSpy is an aggregation platform for vital tracking statistics.
    Config
    Wraps the configuration file for Bukkit.
    DataAggregate
    A data aggregation.
    DataBatcher
    Roughly similar approach to Manager; stage() unwinds data to batch it up, then other task(s) come along to deliver to the database.
    DataListener
    Root abstract class that exemplifies a piece of code that listens to Bukkit events and passes some data along for batching in aggregate.
    DataManager
    Represents a self-monitoring manager that accepts data into a queue and asynchronously pulls data off and handles aggregation; then passes off to the batcher for database insertion
    DataSample
    A data sample; can be destined for aggregation or stand alone.
    DataSampleKey
    Immutable key, used for aggregations
    MultiDataSampler
    Allows samplers to take multiple samples at once; for instance if you want to record the same data against multiple keys.
    PeriodicDataSample
    Simple implementation of a DataSample, this encapuslates a server/world/player (max granularity) sampling of data, done on a distinct period.
    PointDataSample
    Simple implementation of a DataSample, this encapsulates an event's point of data, done on event or demand.
    SingleDataSampler
    Simple single-sampling sampler.
